ed="T" n="0883a19"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0883a19"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>五臺山佛光寺<persName key="A013772">願誠</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0883a20"/><persName key="A013772">釋願誠</persName><ptr target="#n728"/>，姓宋氏。望本<placeName key="PL000000006221">西河</placeName>，家襲<persName key="A002174">素</persName>風<ptr target="#n729"/>，濬流遠<lb
ed="T" n="0883a21"/><anchor xml:id="beg0883sgsz1"/>派<anchor xml:id="end0883sgsz1"/>，不揚<anchor xml:id="beg0883sgsz3"/>胄<anchor xml:id="end0883sgsz3"/>緒，祖考不書。母<persName key="A019505">陰<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>夜夢庭樹對<lb
ed="T" n="0883a22"/>發千<anchor xml:id="beg0883sgsz5"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0883sgsz5"/>，餘<anchor xml:id="beg0883sgsz6"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0883sgsz6"/>尋謝，獨結一果。乃覺有孕。<ref type="person" target="#A019505">母</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0883a23"/>啟願心，得娠男子足矣。十月臨蓐，果如<ref type="person" target="#A019505">其</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0883a24"/>望，立字曰<persName key="A013772">願誠</persName>。後志存小字，不訓法名<lb
ed="T" n="0883a25"/>者，遵慈母之意也。<persName key="A013772">誠</persName>少慕空門，雖為官<lb
ed="T" n="0883a26"/>學生，已有息塵之志。迨棲金地，禮<persName key="A013771">行嚴</persName>為<lb
ed="T" n="0883a27"/>師。<persName key="A013771">嚴</persName>即儒宗珪璋，釋氏師子也。一旦謂<persName key="A013772">誠</persName>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0883a28"/>「<persName key="A013772">汝</persName>神情朗秀，宜於山中，精勤效節，可不務<lb
ed="T" n="0883a29"/>乎！」<date key="j20238892024242" notAfter-iso="+0830-01-31" notBefore-iso="+0829-02-12"><name>大和</name>三年</date>落髮，<date key="j20246272024981" notAfter-iso="+0832-02-09" notBefore-iso="+0831-02-20">五年</date>具戒。先誦諸經，悉<pb ed="T" n="0883b" xml:id="T50.2061.0883b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0883b01"/>皆精練，行人屬耳，道望日隆。無何<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，<date key="j20282682030170" notAfter-iso="+0846-04-25" notBefore-iso="+0841-02-08"><name>會昌</name>中</date>隨<lb
ed="T" n="0883b02"/>例停留，唯<persName key="A013772">誠</persName>志不動搖。及<date key="j20304612035056" to-iso="+0859-09-10" from-iso="+0847-02-10"><name>大中</name></date>再崇釋氏，<lb
ed="T" n="0883b03"/>選定僧員，<persName key="A013772">誠</persName>獨為<anchor xml:id="beg0883sgsz7"/>首<anchor xml:id="end0883sgsz7"/>矣。遂乃重尋<placeName key="PL000000005371">佛光寺</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0883b04"/>已從荒頓，發心次第新成。美聲洋洋，聞於<lb
ed="T" n="0883b05"/><ref type="person" target="#A003667">帝</ref>聽，飈馳聖旨，雲降紫衣。後<ref type="person" target="#A009891">李氏</ref>奄有<placeName key="PL000000003795">并<lb
ed="T" n="0883b06"/>門</placeName>，遐奉<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>，躬遊聖地。覩其令範，撫手愜<lb
ed="T" n="0883b07"/>懷，表聞<ref type="person" target="#A005228">唐天子</ref>，相繼乃賜大師號<persName key="A013772">圓相</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0883b08"/>也，就加山門都檢校。<date key="j20450622045445" notAfter-iso="+0888-02-19" notBefore-iso="+0887-02-01"><name>光啟</name>三載</date>，羞饌命僧捨<lb
ed="T" n="0883b09"/>衣投施。鐘聲引眾，悉至齋堂，右脇曲肱，寂<lb
ed="T" n="0883b10"/>然長往。建塔樹碑<placeName key="PL000000005371">寺</placeName>之西北一里也。</p>
